sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Server
    participant D as Database

    U->>B: Type a new note into the input field
    U->>B: Click "Save" button
    Note right of B: JavaScript event handler captures form data

    B->>S: POST /new_note_spa<br/>Body: {"content": "Note text"}
    Note right of S: Server saves new note to database

    S->>D: INSERT note into database
    D-->>S: Success confirmation

    S-->>B: JSON response {"success": true, "note": {...}}
    Note right of B: Browser updates local note list<br/>and re-renders without page reload
    B-->>U: Updated note list displayed instantly